description: This project is a collection of Windows Phone utility classes that are created or brought together by the Dutch Windows Phone developer community, a loose band of enthousiasts usually referred to as "#wp7nl" or #wpnl (these days) by their twitter hashtag.
summary:
This project is a collection of Windows Phone utility classes that are created or brought together by the Dutch Windows Phone developer community, a loose band of enthousiasts usually referred to as "#wp7nl" or #wpnl (these days) by their twitter hashtag. New version updated for Windows Phone 8.
      3.3.1 is a minor bugfix update in MapShapeDrawBehavior and pulls in new MVVMLight libraries
